title: Black Cat, Gatto Nero 1981 Patrick Magee, Mimsy Farmer, David Warbeck, Al Cliver, Dagmar Lassander, Bruno Corazzari, Daniela Doria, Vito Passeri + Lucio Fulci

sources.title: Black Cat Gatto Nero 1981 Patrick Magee Mimsy Farmer David Warbeck Al Cliver Dag
sources.description: From IMDB: "A professor with the psychic ability to communicate with the dead uses his powers on his pet cat in order to take vengeance upon his enemies." Really pretty much covers it, though it should be noted that somehow the cat can cause car accidents and set rooms on fire. Language is Italian but there are subtitles included.
